  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第四节 理论框架",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_35031-35056",
          "range": "35031-35056",
          "rangeStart": 35031,
          "rangeEnd": 35056,
          "markText": "第二种报复型自杀的经验类型是“威胁性报复型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325191,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:51",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=35031&rangeEnd=35056",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=35031&rangeEnd=35056"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_35420-35445",
          "range": "35420-35445",
          "rangeStart": 35420,
          "rangeEnd": 35445,
          "markText": "第三种报复型自杀的经验类型是“惩罚性报复型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325190,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:50",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=35420&rangeEnd=35445",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=35420&rangeEnd=35445"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_34238-34300",
          "range": "34238-34300",
          "rangeStart": 34238,
          "rangeEnd": 34300,
          "markText": "第三种绝望型自杀的经验类型是“生存性绝望型自杀”。它主要是指人生存所需要的基本的物质性需求得不到满足而自杀的一种绝望型自杀。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325189,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:49",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34238&rangeEnd=34300",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34238&rangeEnd=34300"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_31503-31533",
          "range": "31503-31533",
          "rangeStart": 31503,
          "rangeEnd": 31533,
          "markText": "利己型自杀的第二种经验类型，我将其称作“脱苦性利己型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325188,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:48",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=31503&rangeEnd=31533",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=31503&rangeEnd=31533"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_30692-30762",
          "range": "30692-30762",
          "rangeStart": 30692,
          "rangeEnd": 30762,
          "markText": "对于利己型自杀，我们根据对经验材料的梳理，将其细分为三种类型。一种叫“逃避性利己型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325188,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:48",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=30692&rangeEnd=30762",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=30692&rangeEnd=30762"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_34030-34127",
          "range": "34030-34127",
          "rangeStart": 34030,
          "rangeEnd": 34127,
          "markText": "绝望型自杀的第二种经验类型是“情感性绝望型自杀”。这种自杀类型主要是在自杀行动者的情感需求无法得到满足的情况下而采取自杀的一种绝望型自杀类型，也可以说这种自杀带有“殉情”的特点，但又不完全如此。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325186,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:46",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34030&rangeEnd=34127",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34030&rangeEnd=34127"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_31709-31739",
          "range": "31709-31739",
          "rangeStart": 31709,
          "rangeEnd": 31739,
          "markText": "利己型自杀的第三种经验类型，我将其称为“出气性利己型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325185,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:45",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=31709&rangeEnd=31739",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=31709&rangeEnd=31739"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_32967-32998",
          "range": "32967-32998",
          "rangeStart": 32967,
          "rangeEnd": 32998,
          "markText": "对于绝望型自杀，我们亦可以根据经验材料将其划分为三种经验类型。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325185,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:45",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=32967&rangeEnd=32998",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=32967&rangeEnd=32998"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_34569-34648",
          "range": "34569-34648",
          "rangeStart": 34569,
          "rangeEnd": 34648,
          "markText": "根据经验材料从目的动机的角度出发，我们同样可以将报复型自杀区分为三种经验类型。第一种是“辩诬性报复型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325184,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:44",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34569&rangeEnd=34648",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=34569&rangeEnd=34648"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_10_33204-33229",
          "range": "33204-33229",
          "rangeStart": 33204,
          "rangeEnd": 33229,
          "markText": "第一种绝望型自杀的经验类型是“价值性绝望型自杀”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325181,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:41",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=33204&rangeEnd=33229",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=33204&rangeEnd=33229"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "chapterTitle": "第五章 农民自杀空间化",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_29_1169-1362",
          "range": "1169-1362",
          "rangeStart": 1169,
          "rangeEnd": 1362,
          "markText": "北方区域的农村所不同的地方。从社会结构上来说，这些地域的农村更具有我国中部区域农村的特色。当我在鄂东南的大冶农村、赣南的安远农村调查时，我又能感受到这些地域的农村所具备的与前述两大区域的农村完全不同的地方。从社会结构上来说，这些地域的农村更具备我国南方区域农村的特色。农民的自杀现象在这三大区域的农村中所表现出的迥异的特征分布，勾起了我试图借此来尽可能地理解中国这个巨型社会的强烈兴趣。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325187,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:47",
          "chapterUid": 29,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1169&rangeEnd=1362",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1169&rangeEnd=1362"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_29_1001-1169",
          "range": "1001-1169",
          "rangeStart": 1001,
          "rangeEnd": 1169,
          "markText": "当我在河北省秦皇岛市的农村、山西省河津市的农村、山东省青州市的农村、河南省信阳市的农村以及江苏省淮安市的农村进行调查时，我能够感觉到这些地域鲜明的所谓北方特色，尽管河南信阳与江苏淮安处于南北过渡地带，但从社会结构上来说，这些地域的农村更像是中国的北方区域。当我在江汉平原的荆门农村和孝感农村调查时，我又能深刻地感受到这些地域的农村与前述",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1773325182,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-12 22:19:42",
          "chapterUid": 29,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1001&rangeEnd=1169",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1001&rangeEnd=1169"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "第一节 中国的自杀研究",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_7_4391-4636",
          "range": "4391-4636",
          "rangeStart": 4391,
          "rangeEnd": 4636,
          "markText": "新中国成立60多年来，自杀现象至少有两个明显的时间分野。1949～1980年的30多年中，社会上尽管有自杀现象，但主要是各类精英的政治性自杀。就农村而言，根据我们的田野经验，主要是“历史成分不太清白”的地主的自杀，相反，普通民众的自杀是很少的。20世纪80年代至今的这30多年中，自杀现象突然加剧。农村第一波自杀潮是青年妇女自杀。20世纪90年代中后期尤其是2000年以来，农村年轻女性的自杀已经迅速退潮，农村老年人自杀却掀起了中国人自杀的第二波高潮。为什么会出现这些时间和人群上的变化呢？",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1753192679,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-22 21:57:59",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4636",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4636"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_7_3038-3151",
          "range": "3038-3151",
          "rangeStart": 3038,
          "rangeEnd": 3151,
          "markText": "我认为有三种类型的观点是最值得提及并进行讨论的：第一种是吴飞先生关于中国人自杀的系列文化人类学、哲学等的思考；第二种是华中村治研究群体关于农民自杀的经验思考与社会学思考；第三种是景军教授与张杰教授关于中国自杀现象的社会学分析。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751720755,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-05 21:05:55",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3038&rangeEnd=3151",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3038&rangeEnd=3151"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_7_1051-1166",
          "range": "1051-1166",
          "rangeStart": 1051,
          "rangeEnd": 1166,
          "markText": "历史学方面的研究主要以对1949年以前的自杀现象进行分析为主。从时间段上来看，又主要集中在两个时段：其一，关于清代及以前的女性的自杀现象研究和历史精英的自杀现象研究；其二，关于民初时期的女性的自杀现象研究和知识分子的自杀现象研究。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751720495,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-05 21:01:35",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1051&rangeEnd=1166",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1051&rangeEnd=1166"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 导论",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_6_1418-1537",
          "range": "1418-1537",
          "rangeStart": 1418,
          "rangeEnd": 1537,
          "markText": "上述这些背景材料大致能表明：第一，中国的自杀现象十分严重，至少自有数据公布以来（尤其是整个20世纪90年代），中国在全球属于自杀率偏高的国家；第二，中国的自杀现象具有巨大的城乡差异，要理解中国的自杀现象，就必须深入理解中国农村的自杀现象。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751720410,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-05 21:00:10",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1418&rangeEnd=1537",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/103425e3643425f435777344777344b4739736a36783336783747334d455a76e5b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1418&rangeEnd=1537"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "序一 一部接“地气”的著作",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CWw4Gw4KG9sj6x36x7G3MEZv_4_1428-1478",
          "range": "1428-1478",
          "rangeStart": 1428,
          "rangeEnd": 1478,
          "markText": "在《农民自杀研究》这部著作中，他选取了湖北大冶、湖北应城、河南信阳、河北秦皇岛等地开展多点实地调查。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751468563,
